                    <p class="utterance">. . . I was arrested, and . . . and then . . . later I came to prison, in which I was three weeks. It was near Posen, in Braniewo.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">And so? And afterwards how long were you in Buchenwald?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bernard Warsager</b>
